abstract.text: A view controller for creating, editing, and deleting calendar events.

legalNotices.copyright: Copyright © 2025 Apple Inc. All rights reserved.

inlineContent.text: Presented modally, the event edit view controller provides a way for users to add new events, as well as edit or delete events from their calendar. New events are added to the user’s default calendar unless they choose another calendar in the UI.
